III - Installation
------------------

The installation of libhpnn relies on the autotools system.
Usually only a few steps are required to produce the library:
```
./autogen.sh
./configure
make all
make install
```
The latter may require elevated privileged depending on the installation target directory, which can be modified by the `--prefix=` switch.

For advance instruction and specific combination of compilers or libraries, please see the INSTALL file.

